{{Otheruses|Coruscant Fleet}}
The '''Coruscant Sector Fleet''' was the [[Fleet/Legends|fleet]] of the [[Imperial Navy/Legends|Imperial Navy]] assigned to the [[Coruscant sector/Legends|Coruscant sector]]. For the purposes of [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] naval deployments, Coruscant was considered a sector unto itself.<ref name="SotESb">''[[Shadows of the Empire Sourcebook]]''</ref>

The [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] later had its own [[New Republic First Fleet|Coruscant sector fleet]].<ref name="TLC">''[[The Last Command]]''</ref>

